Code review over a session's file edits

Usage: grs [OPTIONS] [COMMAND]

Commands:
  new          Finalize the current open session and start a new one
  completions  Generate a shell completion script (bash, zsh, fish, elvish, powershell)
  man          Generate a man page (roff) for the `grs` command
  config       View and edit the layered grs config (user / repo / effective)
  help         Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help     Print help
  -V, --version  Print version

Global Options:
  -C, --repo <REPO>    Run as if started in this directory
      --quiet          Suppress status/warning messages (stderr)
      --color <COLOR>  Color output: always | never | auto [possible values: always, never, auto]
      --verbose        Enable debug logging
